## 1.2	系统初始化

### 配置免密登录

```shell
ssh-keygen
ssh-copy-id 192.168.1.11
ssh-copy-id 192.168.1.12
ssh-copy-id 192.168.1.13
ssh-copy-id 192.168.1.14
```



### 主机名配置

```shell
ssh 192.168.1.11 hostnamectl set-hostname kube-master
ssh 192.168.1.12 hostnamectl set-hostname kube-node01
ssh 192.168.1.13 hostnamectl set-hostname kube-node02
ssh 192.168.1.14 hostnamectl set-hostname kube-node03
```

### hosts配置

```
cat >> /etc/hosts << EOF
192.168.1.11 kube-master
192.168.1.12 kube-node01
192.168.1.13 kube-node02
192.168.1.14 kube-node03
EOF

for ip in 192.168.1.12 192.168.1.13 192.168.1.14;do scp /etc/hosts $ip:/etc/ ;done
```



### DNS配置

```shell
cat > /etc/resolv.conf << EOF
nameserver 202.96.134.133
nameserver 114.114.114.114
EOF
for host in kube-master kube-node01 kube-node02 kube-node03 ;do scp /etc/resolv.conf $host:/etc/resolv.conf;done
```



### YUM源配置

```
mkdir /etc/yum.repos.d/backup
mv /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-* /etc/yum.repos.d/backup
curl -o /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo https://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/Centos-7.repo
yum clean all
yum makecache
```



### 关闭firewalld

```
for host in kube-master kube-node01 kube-node02 kube-node03 ;do ssh $host "systemctl disable --now firewalld";done
```



### 关闭selinux

```
setenforce 0
sed -i "s/^SELINUX=enforcing/SELINUX=disabled/g" /etc/sysconfig/selinux
sed -i "s/^SELINUX=enforcing/SELINUX=disabled/g" /etc/selinux/config
sed -i "s/^SELINUX=permissive/SELINUX=disabled/g" /etc/sysconfig/selinux
sed -i "s/^SELINUX=permissive/SELINUX=disabled/g" /etc/selinux/config
reboot
getenforce
```



### 关闭swap分区

```
swapoff -a
cat >> /etc/sysctl.conf << EOF
vm.swappiness = 0
EOF
sysctl -p
cp /etc/fstab{,-bk} && sed -i '/swap/d' /etc/fstab
free -m
```



### 配置时间同步

#### 软件安装

所有服务器都安装

```
yum install -y chrony
```

#### 时间服务器配置

kube-master作为时间服务器

```
cat > /etc/chrony.conf << EOF
server ntp1.aliyun.com iburst
server ntp2.aliyun.com iburst
server ntp3.aliyun.com iburst
driftfile /var/lib/chrony/drift
makestep 1.0 3
rtcsync
allow 192.168.1.0/24
logdir /var/log/chrony
EOF
systemctl start chronyd.service
systemctl enable chronyd.service

chronyc tracking	#显示当前系统的时钟同步状态，包括时间偏差、频率偏移等
chronyc clients		#显示当前连接到 Chrony 的客户端信息
chronyc sourcestats -v		#显示时间服务器的统计信息，包括延迟、偏差等
chronyc activity	#显示当前 Chrony 的活动状态，包括正在使用的服务器数量
```



#### 客户端服务器配置

其它服务器从kube-master同步时间

```
cat > /etc/chrony.conf << EOF
server 192.168.1.11 iburst
driftfile /var/lib/chrony/drift
makestep 1.0 3
rtcsync
logdir /var/log/chrony
EOF
systemctl start chronyd.service
systemctl enable chronyd.service

chronyc sources -v	#显示当前配置的时间服务器及其状态
chronyc tracking	#显示当前系统的时钟同步状态，包括时间偏差、频率偏移等
chronyc makestep		#强制立即同步系统时间，适用于时间偏差较大的情况
```



